public class ECDomainParameters

getByNistECName

public static ECDomainParameters getByNistECName(java.lang.String name)
                                          throws CryptoUtilsException
Get the Domain Parameters for Nist Elliptic Curves using the name of the curve, check static NIST_CURVE_X_### values in this class for supported curves;

Parameters:
name - Name of the curve, as published in FIPS-PUB 186-2
Returns:
EC Domain Parameters of the curve
Throws:
CryptoUtilsException - if the desired curve its not defined
